https://docs.mongodb.com/manual/reference/command/#database-operations

# Create your superuser
$ mongo
> use admin
> db.createUser({user:"adminuser",pwd:"secretpasswd", roles:[{role:"root",db:"admin"}]})
> exit

# Add user to your DB
$ mongo
> use your_db
> db.createUser(
    {
      user: "mongouser",
      pwd: "passwdsecret",
      roles: ["readWrite"]
    }
)




